# 5. Technology Stack

## Frontend
- Framework: React Native 0.81.5 + Expo SDK 54
- Router: Expo Router v6 (file-based)
- State: useState + useCallback + useMemo (אין Redux/Zustand/Context)
- Persistence: AsyncStorage (react-native-async-storage 2.2.0)
- Styling: StyleSheet.create + expo-linear-gradient + expo-blur
- Images: expo-image 3.0.11 (disk cache, contentFit, transition)
- Animations: react-native-reanimated 4.1.1 + react-native-worklets 0.8.3
- Gestures: react-native-gesture-handler 2.28.0
- Build: Metro bundler
- Type checking: TypeScript 5.3

## Backend
- אין — client-only

## Database
- Primary: AsyncStorage (local, JSON blob)
- External (לא פעיל): Supabase Postgres — מוכן לחיבור עתידי

## Infrastructure
- Build: EAS (development / preview APK / production AAB)
- Distribution: Google Play
- אין Terraform, אין Kubernetes, אין Docker

## AI Stack
- Provider: Pollinations.ai
- Model: FLUX (image generation, 1024x1792px)
- Endpoint: https://pollinations.ai/p/{prompt}?width=1024&height=1792&seed={n}&model=flux
- אין embeddings, אין vector DB, אין RAG, אין tool calling

## Monitoring Stack
- כרגע אין כלום — ראה סיכון 1

