# 10. Database Architecture

## Local Storage — AsyncStorage

Key: @football_stars_game
Format: JSON blob יחיד

### GameState Schema
```typescript
{
  appDataVersion: number,        // נוכחי: 5
  onboardingDone: boolean,
  favoriteTeam: string | null,
  playerProgress: {
    [playerId: string]: {
      correctAnswers: number,    // 0-4
      unlocked: boolean,         // true כאשר correctAnswers >= 4
      answeredIndices: number[]  // מונע ספירה כפולה של אותה שאלה
    }
  },
  lineup: {
    gk:  string | null,  // Goalkeeper only
    cb1: string | null,  // Defender only
    cb2: string | null,  // Defender only
    lb:  string | null,  // Defender only
    rb:  string | null,  // Defender only
    cm1: string | null,  // Midfielder | Forward
    cm2: string | null,  // Midfielder | Forward
    cm3: string | null,  // Midfielder | Forward
    lw:  string | null,  // Midfielder | Forward
    rw:  string | null,  // Midfielder | Forward
    st:  string | null   // Midfielder | Forward
  },
  seasonRounds: Round[],
  currentRound: number,
  leagueTable: LeagueRow[],
  coins: number,
  matchStats: { wins: number, draws: number, losses: number },
  aiGenerations: { count: number, lastReset: number },
  streak: {
    current: number,        // ימים רצופים פעילים
    best: number,           // שיא אישי של ימים רצופים
    lastPlayedDate: string  // 'YYYY-MM-DD' — לחישוב רצף
  }
}
```

### Round Schema
```typescript
{ round: number, fixtures: Fixture[] }
```

### Fixture Schema
```typescript
{ home: string, away: string, played: boolean, homeGoals: number|null, awayGoals: number|null }
```

### LeagueRow Schema
```typescript
{ team: string, played: number, wins: number, draws: number, losses: number, gf: number, ga: number, gd: number, pts: number }
```

## Versioning Policy
- appDataVersion חייב להתעדכן בכל שינוי שובר תאימות ל-state schema
- ערך נוכחי: 5
- מיסמץ — DEFAULT_STATE + חזרה ל-onboarding
- חייב להיות זהה ב-hooks/useGameState.ts וב-app/_layout.tsx

